originalText.text:
I had my appointment on December 23rd 2015 at 12p

I was beyond impressed with my time here. Dr. Moyshelis really knew what she was doing and took care of all my needs. She explained everything thoroughly and overall probably THE best eye doctor and service I have ever found.

As far as staff...Aman, who works at the front desk was very professional and helpful with my needs also. With great patience, she answered all of my questions and kindly went over my options with me. I definitely recommend this place and will be going back in January ! :)
